 27/2/18 Sell Had an earli lunch and then rode out with Grove and Smith to reconnoitr the ground for tomorrow 's oper . Return to the footbal ground march in rear of the 24th . A great crowd at the footbal ground where they beat us after a good game . Great excit and barrack . Col . Durran , Gener Paton other were on the ground . Word came to hand that our demonstr platoon under Gorman had won the Brigad Championship . Veri pleas about this win . Arrang all detail for our oper tomorrow . Some rain came on just befor mess . Sutherland Barker Abercrombi go on leav tomorrow
